data.description: Experience comfortable living in this impeccable 3-bed, 2-bath home, nestled on a serene cul-de-sac corner lot. The well-designed layout offers ample space and warmth, seamlessly connecting living areas for relaxation and entertainment to include a FRESH COAT OF INTERIOR PAINT !!!! A covered patio beckons for morning coffees or tranquil evenings, while nearby BISD schools can  ensure convenience and quality education. This captivating home promises a life of contentment, blending indoor and outdoor living seamlessly. Don't miss out on this prime opportunity.
